import React from 'react'
import { Segment, SegmentGroup } from 'semantic-ui-react'


const Card = ({ children }) => {
  
  return (
    <SegmentGroup>
      <Segment> {children} </Segment>
      <Segment.Group>
        <Segment>Nested Top</Segment>
        <Segment>Nested Middle</Segment>
        <Segment>Nested Bottom</Segment>
      </Segment.Group>
    </SegmentGroup>
  )
  
}

export default Card
